high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to the toaster on the counter.
Pick up the plate which is to the left of the toaster.
Heat the plate in the microwave for a few seconds, then take it out and close the microwave.
Put the plate back on the counter in its original position.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot plate on a counter top.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter then take a step left.
Pick up the plate that's in front of you to the left of the toaster.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Warm the plate in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Turn right to face the counter by the toaster again.
Put the plate back where you got it.
anns.task_desc: Put a a warm plate on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to face the counter.
Pick up the plate on the counter.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Heat the plate in the microwave.
Turn right to face the counter.
Place the plate on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To heat a plate and place it on the counter.
